    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super reliable, and honestly still drives like a dream. I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, and it\u2019s just looking for a new home and its next big adventure. If you're looking for a dependable car that looks great and won't let you down, this is the one! Feel free to reach out\u2014I'd love for you to come take it for a spin!",
