    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Up for sale is a vehicle that perfectly embodies the 'well-loved daily driver.' The exterior is finished in a timeless coat that still holds a deep, reflective gloss, though a close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front fascia and a small, shallow scratch near the trunk lid\u2014standard signs of highway travel. The wheels are wrapped in tires with plenty of tread remaining, and the brakes were serviced just last season. Inside, the cabin is remarkably clean and has never been smoked in. The leather upholstery is soft and intact, showing only light creasing on the driver\u2019s side bolster. All interior electronics, including the infotainment screen, heated seats, and sunroof, operate flawlessly. Mechanically, the car is in its prime; the engine idles quietly and provides smooth, consistent power under acceleration, while the transmission shifts are seamless. I have kept a meticulous log of oil changes and routine maintenance to ensure it remains reliable for years to come. This is a solid, honest car for someone who appreciates quality without the showroom-new price tag.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
      "firm_id": "sybil_5",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this meticulously maintained vehicle, offering a superb balance of performance and sophistication. This unit has undergone a comprehensive professional inspection to ensure mechanical integrity and long-term reliability. The exterior retains a commendable finish, while the interior cabin reflects a high standard of care and cleanliness. An ideal acquisition for the professional seeking a dependable, high-caliber driving experience without compromise.",
      "price": 34800.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! \ud83d\udc4b I'm looking to find a new home for my trusty ride. It\u2019s been a fantastic car and is still in really solid shape\u2014perfect for someone who wants a reliable daily driver that looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, so it's ready to hit the pavement as soon as you are. Would love for you to come by, take it for a spin, and see if it's the right fit for you!",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
