      "timestep_posted": 42
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a mechanically sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) powered by the iconic S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring six individual throttle bodies and a 8,000 RPM redline. This example is equipped with the desirable Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential. Critical preventive maintenance has been addressed, including rear subframe reinforcement and a comprehensive Vanos system overhaul to ensure optimal variable valve timing. The chassis remains taut with refreshed bushings and factory-spec damping, providing the communicative steering and balanced turn-in synonymous with the M-division's peak analog era. While the exterior shows minor age-appropriate wear, the drivetrain and cooling system are in excellent health, making this a turn-key performance machine for the discerning driver.",
